Disable Cortana Service

Start Menu > Services > Windows Search
Disable service
Stop Service
Apply

Disable Cortana Registry

Start Menu > Regedit.exe
KEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\Windows Search
Create DWORD Value "AllowCortana" = 0

Block Search/Cortana at F/W

Start Menu > Windows Defender Firewall with Advanced Security > Inbound Rules
Block Cortana and Windows Shell Experience
